MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 82

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE KIMAGANGO NATIONAL HIGH SCHOOL A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE BARANGAY OF KIMAGANGO, MUNICIPALITY OF MIDSAYAP, PROVINCE OF COTABATO, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, FIDEL V. RAMOS, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale or settlement and reserve for school site purposes of the Kimagango National High School, under the administration of the Secretary of Education, Culture and Sports, subject to private rights, if any there be, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in the barangay of Kimagango, Municipality of Midsayap, Province of Cotabato, Island of Mindanao, which parcel is more particularly described as follows, to wit:

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot No. 593-A, Csd-12-004694-D being a portion of Lot 593, Pls-134), situated in the Barangay of Kimagango, Municipality of Midsayap, Province of Cotabato, Island of Mindanao, Bounded on the S., along line 1-2 by Lot 593-H, Csd-004694-D; on the SW., along lines 2-3-4-5 by Road (Lot 593-1, Csd-12-004694-D); on the SW., W. & N., along lines 5-6-7-8 by Lot 593-J, Csd-12-004694-D; and on the NE. & E., along line 8-9-10-1 by Lot 593-H, Csd-12-004694-D. Beginning at a point marked “1” on the plan being S. 39° 03’E., 2564.77 m. from BLLM #4, Pls-134, Midsayap Public Land Subdivision. Thence . . .

78.23 m. to point 2;

12.24 m. to point 3;

69.12 m. to point 4;

33.69 m. to point 5;

70.40 m. to point 6;

100.00 m. to point 7;

102.43 m. to point 8;

75.32 m. to point 9;

107.73 m. to point 10;

91.37 m. to point of

Beginning, containing an area of EIGHTEEN THOUSAND FOUR HUNDRED TWENTY-THREE (18,423) SQUARE METERS.

All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. Cyl. Conc. Mons. Bearing true. Date of original survey was on October 1920 and that of the subdivision survey on September 21, 1989 executed by Teodorico B. Junio, Geodetic Engineer, and approved on October 19, 1989.

Note: This lot is equivalent to Lot 3301, a portion of Lot 593, Pls-134.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 27th day of October, in the year of Our Lord, nineteen hundred and ninety-two.

(Sgd.) FIDEL V. RAMOS

By the President: (Sgd.) EDELMIRO A. AMANTE, SR. Executive Secretary

